  <h2 class="underline">Contributions</h2>
  <ul>
      <li><a href="https://bray.tech" aria-label="Braytech" title="Braytech" target="_blank">Braytech <Icon size={10} name="mdi:external-link" /></a> (Translator):
          View & map checklists, track & view triumphs, inspect collectibles, and much more!</li>
      <li><a href="https://destinyitemmanager.com/" aria-label="Destiny Item Manager" title="Destiny Item Manager" target="_blank">Destiny Item Manager <Icon size={10} name="mdi:external-link" /></a> (Translator):
