      <li><a href="https://github.com/solelychloe/enlive" title="ENLiVE.media">ENLiVE <Icon size={10} name="mdi:external-link" /></a> (Website Developer, March - July 2020): 
          ENLiVE is a English and Japanese VTuber group.</li>
      <li><a href="https://hibiki.app/" title="Hibiki">Hibiki <Icon size={10} name="mdi:external-link" /></a> (Lead Developer, September 2018 - August 2019): 
          The best all-in-one Discord bot! Automod, fun, music, utilities, and more.</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/jiktim" title="jiktim">jiktim <Icon size={10} name="mdi:external-link" /></a> (Contributor, August 2016 - 2019): 
